                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipit of Text I; initial lines (one or two first lines) of prayers; names of Ethiopian prelates; directives for the ministers; some separated letters of nomina sacra (fols. 38ra); elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
 &#xD;
